- Read, listen to &amp; watch more than 15,000 books, audio and video clips about Islam

- Share via Facebook, Twitter, Email and Messages

- More than 45 languages available

- Print books via AirPrint

- Stream videos to watch immediately and save space on device

- Download full books and videos in the background to read/watch them offline

- Continue listening to audio or video clips in the background after closing the app

- New content continuously added, refresh to get more

- Content is organized into categories for easier access

- All FREE content

- Renowned Islamic scholars: Bilal Philips, Yusuf Estes, Ahmed Deedat, Zakir Naik

